{
  "info": {
    "name": "Hify · App 应用管理（第1轮）",
    "description": "对话型应用元数据 CRUD + 团队共享权限 + 启停 的接口测试集。\n\n路由族：成员族 /api/v1/app/apps/**（任意登录用户可访问；改/删/启停的 owner+Admin 限制在 service 层判，越权回 403/10004）。\n\n用法：\n1. 先跑「0. 登录(admin)」拿 token（自动存入集合变量 token，后续请求自动带 Bearer）。\n2. 顺序跑「主流程」1→9：创建会把返回 id 存入 appId，供详情/更新/启停/删除复用。\n3. 「反例」组可单独跑（多数自带创建/不依赖删除）。\n4. 「权限矩阵」组是自包含的：它自己用 admin 建一个 app，再用 member 账号验越权 403 与全员可见 —— 需先准备一个 member 账号，并在集合变量填 memberUsername/memberPassword（建账号见 admin-user-management.postman_collection.json）。\n\n约定：响应是 Result 信封 {code,message,data,traceId}；成功 code=200；id/modelId/ownerId 一律序列化为字符串；列表是 PageResult {list,total,page,size}；config 为 jsonb，本轮仅 systemPrompt。\n\n本轮范围提醒：modelId 只存不校（等 provider C 才校模型是否存在），type 仅放行 chat（workflow→16001），type 创建后不可改（更新无 type 字段）。",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    { "key": "baseUrl", "value": "http://localhost:8080" },
    { "key": "adminUsername", "value": "admin" },
    { "key": "adminPassword", "value": "change-me-on-first-deploy" },
    { "key": "memberUsername", "value": "member1" },
    { "key": "memberPassword", "value": "change-me" },
    { "key": "token", "value": "" },
    { "key": "memberToken", "value": "" },
    { "key": "appId", "value": "" },
    { "key": "permAppId", "value": "" }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "0. 登录(admin) → 存 token",
      "request": {
        "auth": { "type": "noauth" },
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/identity/login",
          "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
          "path": [ "api", "v1", "identity", "login" ]
        },
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"username\": \"{{adminUsername}}\",\n  \"password\": \"{{adminPassword}}\"\n}"
        }
      },
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "type": "text/javascript",
            "exec": [
              "const json = pm.response.json();",
              "pm.test('登录成功 code=200', () => pm.expect(json.code).to.eql(200));",
              "pm.test('返回 token', () => pm.expect(json.data.token).to.be.a('string').and.not.empty);",
              "pm.collectionVariables.set('token', json.data.token);"
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "主流程（按顺序跑 1→9）",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. 创建-对话型 → 存 appId",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app/apps",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "app", "apps" ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"客服问答助手\",\n  \"description\": \"基于知识库的对话应用\",\n  \"type\": \"chat\",\n  \"modelId\": null,\n  \"config\": { \"systemPrompt\": \"你是一名友好的客服助手。\" }\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('code=200', () => pm.expect(j.code).to.eql(200));",
                  "pm.test('type=chat', () => pm.expect(j.data.type).to.eql('chat'));",
                  "pm.test('状态默认 enabled', () => pm.expect(j.data.status).to.eql('enabled'));",
                  "pm.test('id 为字符串', () => pm.expect(j.data.id).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "pm.test('ownerId 为字符串(=当前 admin)', () => pm.expect(j.data.ownerId).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "pm.test('config.systemPrompt 往返一致', () => pm.expect(j.data.config.systemPrompt).to.eql('你是一名友好的客服助手。'));",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('appId', j.data.id);"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "2. 列表（分页 + 字段断言）",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app/apps?page=1&size=20",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "app", "apps" ],
              "query": [
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "20" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('code=200', () => pm.expect(j.code).to.eql(200));",
                  "pm.test('PageResult 结构 list/total/page/size', () => { pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('list'); pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('total'); pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('page'); pm.expect(j.data).to.have.property('size'); });",
                  "pm.test('list 是数组', () => pm.expect(j.data.list).to.be.an('array'));",
                  "if (j.data.list.length) { pm.test('行 id 为字符串', () => pm.expect(j.data.list[0].id).to.be.a('string')); }"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "3. 列表-按关键字筛选",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app/apps?keyword=客服&page=1&size=20",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "app", "apps" ],
              "query": [
                { "key": "keyword", "value": "客服" },
                { "key": "page", "value": "1" },
                { "key": "size", "value": "20" }
              ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('code=200', () => pm.expect(j.code).to.eql(200));",
                  "pm.test('命中至少一条', () => pm.expect(j.data.list.length).to.be.above(0));",
                  "pm.test('命中名含关键字', () => pm.expect(j.data.list[0].name).to.include('客服'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "4. 详情",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app/apps/{{appId}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "app", "apps", "{{appId}}" ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('code=200', () => pm.expect(j.code).to.eql(200));",
                  "pm.test('id 匹配', () => pm.expect(j.data.id).to.eql(pm.collectionVariables.get('appId')));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "5. 更新（改名+改 systemPrompt，验 config 往返）",
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app/apps/{{appId}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "app", "apps", "{{appId}}" ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"客服问答助手(已改)\",\n  \"description\": \"更新后的描述\",\n  \"modelId\": null,\n  \"config\": { \"systemPrompt\": \"改写后的人设。\" }\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('code=200', () => pm.expect(j.code).to.eql(200));",
                  "pm.test('名称已更新', () => pm.expect(j.data.name).to.eql('客服问答助手(已改)'));",
                  "pm.test('config 已更新', () => pm.expect(j.data.config.systemPrompt).to.eql('改写后的人设。'));",
                  "pm.test('type 不可改仍为 chat', () => pm.expect(j.data.type).to.eql('chat'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "6. 禁用",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app/apps/{{appId}}/disable",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "app", "apps", "{{appId}}", "disable" ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('code=200', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().code).to.eql(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "7. 启用",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app/apps/{{appId}}/enable",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "app", "apps", "{{appId}}", "enable" ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('code=200', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().code).to.eql(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "8. 删除（逻辑删除）",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app/apps/{{appId}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "app", "apps", "{{appId}}" ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('code=200', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().code).to.eql(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "9. 删除幂等（再删同一 id 仍 200）",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app/apps/{{appId}}",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "app", "apps", "{{appId}}" ]
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('删不存在的也算成功 code=200', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().code).to.eql(200));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "反例（可单独跑，先跑 0.登录）",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "反例 · 创建 type=workflow（期望 400/16001）",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app/apps",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "app", "apps" ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"工作流应用(不该建成)\",\n  \"type\": \"workflow\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('HTTP 400', () => pm.response.to.have.status(400));",
                  "pm.test('业务码 16001', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().code).to.eql(16001));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "反例 · 创建缺 name（期望 400/10001）",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app/apps",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "app", "apps" ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"\",\n  \"type\": \"chat\"\n}"
            }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('HTTP 400', () => pm.response.to.have.status(400));",
                  "const j = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.test('业务码 10001', () => pm.expect(j.code).to.eql(10001));",
                  "pm.test('data 是字段错误数组', () => pm.expect(j.data).to.be.an('array'));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "反例 · 重名创建（期望 409/10006）",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "prerequest",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "// 先建一个固定名的 app（若已存在则下面创建直接撞 409，也算通过）",
                  "const base = pm.collectionVariables.get('baseUrl');",
                  "const token = pm.collectionVariables.get('token');",
                  "pm.sendRequest({ url: base + '/api/v1/app/apps', method: 'POST', header: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + token }, body: { mode: 'raw', raw: JSON.stringify({ name: '重名测试-固定', type: 'chat' }) } }, function () {});"
                ]
              }
            },
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "type": "text/javascript",
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('HTTP 409', () => pm.response.to.have.status(409));",
                  "pm.test('业务码 10006', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().code).to.eql(10006));"
                ]
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [ { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" } ],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/v1/app/apps",
              "host": [ "{{baseUrl}}" ],
              "path": [ "api", "v1", "app", "apps" ]
            },
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"重名测试-固定\",\n  \"type\": \"chat\"\n}"
            }
          }
        },
